## Available Themes

| Theme ID | Brand | Key Difference |
|---|---|---|
| `walmart` (default) | Walmart | Blue brand colors |
| `bodega` | Bodega | Green brand colors |
| `walmart-legacy` | Walmart (Bogle font) | Green SubNav + Bogle typography |
| `sams-club` | Sam's Club | Sam's Club brand colors |
| `developer` | Developer/Debug | Token debug view |

