## Common Semantic Tokens by Category

### Brand Colors (theme-sensitive — these WILL change per theme)
```css
--ld-semantic-color-fill-brand-subtle     /* Subtle brand fill (SubNav, banners) */
--ld-semantic-color-fill-brand-bold       /* Bold brand fill */
--ld-semantic-color-text-brand            /* Brand body text */
--ld-semantic-color-text-brand-bold       /* Bold brand text (headers, labels) */
--ld-semantic-color-border-brand          /* Brand borders */
--ld-semantic-color-border-brand-bold     /* Bold brand borders */
```

### Action Colors (mapped to brand — these WILL change per theme for action tints)
```css
--ld-semantic-color-action-fill-primary            /* Primary button fill */
--ld-semantic-color-action-fill-primary-hovered
--ld-semantic-color-action-fill-primary-pressed
--ld-semantic-color-action-text-on-fill-primary    /* Text ON primary button */
--ld-semantic-color-action-focus-outline
```

### Surface / Fill (generally stable)
```css
--ld-semantic-color-surface                /* Default surface (white) */
--ld-semantic-color-fill-subtle            /* Subtle fill (light gray) */
--ld-semantic-color-fill-inverse           /* Dark/inverse fill */
--ld-semantic-color-fill-accent-blue-subtle /* Accent blue-subtle (not brand) */
```

### Text (generally stable)
```css
--ld-semantic-color-text                   /* Primary text */
--ld-semantic-color-text-subtle            /* Secondary/muted text */
--ld-semantic-color-text-inverse           /* Text on dark background */
--ld-semantic-color-text-onfill-brand      /* Text on brand-filled surface */
--ld-semantic-color-text-onfill-inverse    /* Text on inverse-filled surface */
```

### Spacing (stable — does not change per theme)
```css
--ld-semantic-spacing-50     /* 4px */
--ld-semantic-spacing-100    /* 8px */
--ld-semantic-spacing-200    /* 16px */
--ld-semantic-spacing-300    /* 24px */
--ld-semantic-spacing-400    /* 32px */
--ld-semantic-spacing-component-padding-small   /* 8px */
--ld-semantic-spacing-component-padding-medium  /* 12px */
--ld-semantic-spacing-component-padding-large   /* 16px */
```

### Typography (stable — does not change per theme)
```css
--ld-semantic-font-family-sans
--ld-semantic-font-body-small-size         /* 0.875rem / 14px */
--ld-semantic-font-body-small-weight-default /* 400 */
--ld-semantic-font-body-small-weight-alt   /* 700 */
--ld-semantic-font-body-small-line-height
--ld-semantic-font-body-medium-size        /* 1rem / 16px */
--ld-semantic-font-body-large-size
--ld-semantic-font-heading-small-size
--ld-semantic-font-heading-medium-size
--ld-semantic-font-heading-large-size
```

